        "Description": "Greetings 47. A blood gem smuggling group known as the Quilboar Quartet, known worldwide for their heinous mining operations in central Africa, have quietly assumed new identities here in Whittleton Creek, where they plan to start pawning off product. Why not give them a metallic taste of their own medicine? (blood) (the medicine is blood)",
